@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Оформление подписки

actor User
participant "Web App" as Web
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Subscription Service" as SubService
participant "Payment System" as Payment
participant "Database" as DB
queue "Kafka" as Kafka

User -> Web: Нажать "Оформить подписку"
Web -> Gateway: POST /subscriptions
Gateway -> SubService: Forward request

SubService -> DB: Проверить пользователя
DB --> SubService: User data

SubService -> Payment: POST /charges
Payment --> SubService: Payment confirmed

SubService -> DB: Создать подписку
DB --> SubService: Subscription created

SubService -> Kafka: Publish event "subscription.created"
SubService --> Gateway: 201 Created
Gateway --> Web: Response
Web --> User: Подписка оформлена

@enduml
